  "text": "In case of depressed women that only performed aerobic exercises, our results were consistent with the results of the studies conducted by Martinson et al [CITATION_1] and Zarshenas et al [CITATION_2] , showing that performance of aerobic exercise alone does not exert positive effect on the depression of these depressed women.",
